---
title: Truffle & Mushroom Risotto with Cucumber & Pear Salad
description: This comforting mushroom risotto becomes rich and full of flavour with truffle oil and Parmesan. Add a crisp cucumber and pear salad and roasted hazelnuts to perfectly round out the meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/truffle-mushroom-risotto-c41d7261.jpg
